      "title": "Curriculum Theory, Didaktik, and Educational Leadership: Reflections on the Foundations of the Research Program",
      "authors": [
        {
          "name": "Rose M. Ylimaki",
          "openalex_id": "A5086460570",
          "orcid": "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1217-4185",
